      "title": "Two important things about passwords",
      "point1": {
        "title": "1. One password per account",
        "description": "Imagine: If you use the same key for both your house and your safe, when a thief gets the key, they can access everything. Passwords are the same - each account should have a unique password!"
      },
      "point2": {
        "title": "2. Passwords must be truly random",
